\begin_layout Abstract
Ah hah! I solved it! The problem of free will! Or rather, I have found a
 solution that I am happy with.
 Your milage may vary.
 The answer is rather mathematical, and if you do not have a formal education
 in mathematics and physics, and if you do not have long hands-on working
 exprience with dynamical systems, you won't much like it.
 The answer is perhaps 
